lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCARI2g7r-PHaxrIcAYsMfmA&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y9WqQ%2Br5Wu6dnGlIIIMUdw0%3D&h=3a7a4e14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCARI2g7r-PHaxrIcAYsMfmA</a><br />\nYuNi - virtual singer<span class=\"pink\"> (主打唱歌)</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DGN3Dor.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDGN3Dor.png&h=22ec656e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCHTnX0CSX_KObo5I9WuZ64g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCHTnX0CSX_KObo5I9WuZ64g&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y9WqQ%2Br5Wu6dnGlIIIMUdw0%3D&h=2c2272f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCHTnX0CSX_KObo5I9WuZ64g</a><br />\n<br />\nバーチャルおばあちゃんねる <span class=\"pink\">(虛擬婆婆)</span> (vtuber界痴線代表之一)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sSuJDoG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsSuJDoG.jpg&h=c82dec2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCTMgd9qnUD9qKBX5oTtD6ug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCTMgd9qnUD9qKBX5oTtD6ug&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y9WqQ%2Br5Wu6dnGlIIIMUdw0%3D&h=d2726d7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCTMgd9qnUD9qKBX5oTtD6ug</a><br />\n<br />\n星乃めあ <span class=\"pink\">(主打唱歌)</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.moguravr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/201908051805291000.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moguravr.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F201908051805291000.jpg&h=eb111ba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCsiKFVHkQSMlSe0vaCG0anw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCsiKFVHkQSMlSe0vaCG0anw&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y9WqQ%2Br5Wu6dnGlIIIMUdw0%3D&h=700647e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCsiKFVHkQSMlSe0vaCG0anw</a><br />\n最近有唔少日本傳統企業開始推出vtuber,<br />\n而且好多nico大手都開始轉生做vtuber<br />\n<br />\nSUNTORY三得利  燦鳥ノム<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sPpxwKh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsPpxwKh.jpg&h=e1cd9f40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCwRKt_raV3N5KZgxcFyC1vw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCwRKt_raV3N5KZgxcFyC1vw&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y9WqQ%2Br5Wu6dnGlIIIMUdw0%3D&h=dee373bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCwRKt_raV3N5KZgxcFyC1vw</a><br />\n樂敦製藥<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCnDZwUFMzqOBcF3bjRfZD-g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCnDZwUFMzqOBcF3bjRfZD-g&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y9WqQ%2Br5Wu6dnGlIIIMUdw0%3D&h=06f8c30a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCnDZwUFMzqOBcF3bjRfZD-g</a><br />\n<br />\nウェザーニュース ウェザーロイド Airi（ポン子）<br />\nweathernews既天氣主播, 2012年開始以3D登場,主要職責係天氣預報節目播報天氣,<br />\n係vtuber一詞未出現前就進行類似既直播.曾因節目方針改面一度面臨廢棄危機,但適逢vtuber潮流開始興起,同埋過往一d直播精華備受關注,知名度上升,因此得以以vtuber名義繼續活動,報導天氣資訊.2018年5月開設youtube帳號<br />\n<span class=\"pink\">經理人為社內資歷最深主播山岸愛梨.</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/weatheroidAiriChannel/videos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2FweatheroidAiriChannel%2Fvideos&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y9WqQ%2Br5Wu6dnGlIIIMUdw0%3D&h=8a4387e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/c/weatheroidAiriChannel/videos</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DjiCDtF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDjiCDtF.jpg&h=16baa754&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有部分知名作品既角色都以vtuber出現 <br />\n有時係由原作既聲優配音,多數目標係宣傳個作品,<br />\n例如妹妹公主,小雙俠,馬娘, ハート様<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oYz6N9q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoYz6N9q.jpg&h=6d518ac0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pc61B2L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpc61B2L.jpg&h=faa25e5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uh9uLWr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUh9uLWr.jpg&h=d8d3b743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除左以短片為主亦都有以生放用(live)為主既vtuber<br />\n<br />\n講起開live就唔可以唔講<span class=\"red\">にじさんじ</span> (彩虹社)<br />\n<img src=\"https://secure-dcdn.cdn.nimg.jp/nicochannel/material/design/4067553/1223KVTOP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsecure-dcdn.cdn.nimg.jp%2Fnicochannel%2Fmaterial%2Fdesign%2F4067553%2F1223KVTOP.png&h=0f2ba982&s={SIZE}\" /><p class=\"left\"><p class=\"left\"></p></p>"},{"pid":"50f7c31a546b6fec9d8a99c749f9ace98af4b8c6","tid":2279366,"uid":33651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T17:31:55.000Z","msg":"4個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ac29f2163ebe94a94e9d760a1803f919c7efac","tid":2279366,"uid":256957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T17:32:38.000Z","msg":"推呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2279365/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2279365/page/1</a>"}],"pinned":{"pid":"63ac29f2163ebe94a94e9d760a1803f919c7efac","tid":2279366,"uid":256957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T17:32:38.000Z","msg":"推呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2279365/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2279365/page/1</a>"}}